Clean="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-GB" sz="2300" dirty="0" smtClean="0"/><a:t>Some </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-GB" sz="2300" dirty="0"/><a:t>factors leading to this phenomenon includes: rising healthcare costs, long travel distances to health facilities, and easy access to over-the-counter medicines. </a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr lang="en-GB" sz="2300" dirty="0" smtClean="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-GB" sz="2300" dirty="0" smtClean="0"/><a:t>Since </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-GB" sz="2300" dirty="0"/><a:t>this practice is unlikely to disappear, it presents an opportunity to make self-care safer, accessible, guided, and affordable</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-GB" sz="2300" dirty="0" smtClean="0"/><a:t>.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-GB" sz="2300" dirty="0"/><a:t>The </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-GB" sz="2300" dirty="0" err="1"/><a:t>Tobinco</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-GB" sz="2300" dirty="0"/><a:t> </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-GB" sz="2300" dirty="0" err="1"/><a:t>EmergencyCare</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-GB" sz="2300" dirty="0"/><a:t> Kit Initiative proposes the development and nationwide distribution of a branded, standardized first aid and minor-ailment care kit for homes, schools, and workplaces.</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="2300" dirty="0"/></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp></p:spTree><p:extLst><p:ext uri="{BB962C8B-B14F-4D97-AF65-F5344CB8AC3E}"><p14:creationId xmlns:p14="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/powerpoint/2010/main" val="1231881664"/></p:ext></p:extLst></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr><p:transition spd="slow"><p:push dir="u"/></p:transition><p:timing><p:tnLst><p:par><p:cTn id="1" dur="indefinite" restart="never" nodeType="tmRoot"><p:childTnLst><p:seq concurrent="1" nextAc="seek"><p:cTn id="2" dur="indefinite" nodeType="mainSeq"><p:childTnLst><p:par><p:cTn id="3" fill="hold"><p:stCondLst><p:cond delay="indefinite"/></p:stCondLst><p:childTnLst><p:par><p:cTn id="4" fill="hol